'''Girley Charlene Jazama''' ni umukinnyi wa filime wa [[Namibiya]], umwanditsi w'amafilime akaba na producer wa firime . <ref name="Nam">https://www.namibian.com.na/204283/archive-read/Girley-Jazama-bags-Sotigui-nomination</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Umwuga wa Jazama wamafirime namakinamico watangiye kuva muri 2005. Yabaye Namibiya wa kabiri watowe muri ''Sotigui Awards'', nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza, nyuma ya Adriano Visagie wari watowe mbere kubera igitaramo cye muri " ''[[Salute! (film)|Salute!]]'' ", Aratsinda. 

Yagaragaye cyane mu bakinnyi bari muri "''The Lion King'' ", mu gihe yari yarize mu ishuri ryigenga rya Karibib. 

Yakoranye umwete ku bufatanye na Pan-African Festival ya Sinema na Televiziyo ya [[Wagadugu|Ouagadougou]], mu rwego rwo kumenyekanisha impano mu gukina sinema nyafurika na diaspora.  <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202009090959.html</ref>

Mu mwaka wa 2008, yari umwe mu banditsi barindwi batoranijwe na sosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa, Optimedia, kugira ngo yandike isabune nshya yise ''"Amasano ahuza"'', ku kigo cya Namibia Broadcasting Corporation. <ref>https://www.balancingact-africa.com/news/broadcast-en/11379/technology-convergence-in-brief</ref> Uyu musaruro wabaye televiziyo ya mbere ya Namibiya. <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/200804300386.html</ref>

Mu 2009, yakinnye nka "Schülerin" muri filime yo [[Ikidage|mu kidage]] '', "Liebe, Babys und der Zauber Afrikas'' ". <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt1383245/fullcredits/cast?ref_=m_ttfc_3</ref> <ref>https://www.networkmovie.de/en/liebe-babys-und-der-zauber-afrikas/</ref> <ref>https://agilebc.ma/journal/liebe%2C-babys-und-der-zauber-afrikas-9d38f1</ref>

Jazama yari umukinnyi wa mbere muri firime ya 2019, " ''Umurongo Wera'' " aho yakinnye nka "Sylvia". <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201907260574.html</ref> <ref>https://www.namibian.com.na/178013/archive-read/Behind-&ampamp39The-White-Line&ampamp39</ref> Muri Nyakanga 2019, iyi filime yerekanwe ku rwego mpuzamahanga mu iserukiramuco rya sinema mpuzamahanga rya 40 rya Durban ndetse no mu yandi maserukiramuco menshi ya firime ku isi. <ref>https://economist.com.na/56433/after-hours/the-white-line-to-premiere-at-ster-kinekor-theatres-in-november/</ref>

Filime ye ya 2019 yiminota 29, ''Baxu and the Giants'' yakoranye na Andrew Botelle kandi iyobowe na Florian Schott, <ref>https://www.dhps-windhoek.de/post/joint-project-a-huge-success-nwg-news-and-dhps-alumni-association-hand-over-donation-to-save-the-rhino-trust</ref> yizihijwe ninganda za firime za Namibiya nka firime ya mbere ya Namibiya kuri Netflix . <ref>https://www.erongo.com.na/news/baxu-breaks-boundaries2020-09-15</ref> Muri Werurwe 2020, iyi filime yatowe mu ''iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi RapidLion ryabereye'' i Johannesburg, [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] igihembo cya "Filime Nziza Nziza". <ref>https://thestreetjournal.org/2020/09/namibia-first-local-short-film-debuts-on-netflix/</ref> Nyuma yerekanwe muri [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|Amerika]] mu ''iserukiramuco rya sinema ryigenga rya San Francisco'' hanyuma nyuma muri Nzeri muri uwo mwaka muri ''Namibian Theatre & Film Awards 2019'', aho yakiriye nomination zirindwi. <ref>https://confidentenamibia.com/baxu-and-the-giants-nominated-at-ntfa/</ref> Nanone, filime yakiriye izindi nomination n'ibihembo. <ref>https://afrykamera.pl/en/program/afroshortsspirituality/x</ref>

